body: Don't read this as a review. Just sharing my personal experience with the product and I hope you would like it. Before I start here are some key features of the product :ðŸ“¢ Bluetooth 5.0ðŸ“¢ Extra BassðŸ“¢ Built in powerbankðŸ“¢ Can be connected to two different devicesðŸ“¢ Charges quickIn Box Content1. Two piece earbuds2. Built in Powerbank3. Charging cable4. Carrying pouch5. User ManualðŸ¤— MY EXPERIENCE,ðŸ¤—Got this delivered a week ago and writing this review today on 26th March. Certain things I have liked and certain disliked. So let's start with the positive. Uniquely built, the build quality of these buds are premium and you can feel that the moment you hold this in your hand. The built in Powerbank is an added advantage. It can charge the buds and also your phone in emergency. Though the capacity is 3000Mah but it works wonders when you are out and your phone is running low on battery. The best part is that things are automatic. The moment you place the buds in the charging case, it automatically starts charging and disconnect when fully charged. So now no worry of overcharging. Now let's talk about the sound output. Initially I was little sceptic but these beauties have proved me wrong. Amazingly balanced sound and excellent BASS. Very very very satisfied by the sound output.  Connectivity wise these are equipped with BLUETOOTH 5.0 and the range is very good. Approximately at around 20 metre, the buds were working great.Enough of Likes, now let's talk about the dislikes. Due to inbuilt Powerbank, the feel is little bulky, but as said earlier, it can save you from disaster at times. You know phones are life now....HahahaSecondly was expecting a charging adapter with these but again, since it is universally accepted USB 3.0  one can use any charging adapter.That's the end of my experience with this product and I can assure you that if you are okay with two dislikes I have spoken of, you will be much more than satisfied with these beauties. They are much better than the branded ones and the Powerbank is again , a life saving feature .Thanks for your time.

body: Very good quality earphones. Reviewing after 3 Day of usage.SOUND QUALITY : The sound quality is very crisp. The highs and lows are nicely balanced. Overall pretty good at this price. The sound is loud enough as well. I personally, barely go above 50-60%. The latter being better. Using a Bluetooth 5.0 capable phone One Plus 5, I just loved the music. Although the sound leaks at very high volume and other people know what you're listening to.BATTERY LIFE : The battery life is good. It gives almost 4.5-5 hrs of backup at 50-60% volume. This is pretty good considering we have a charging case that can charge the buds 12-15 times.BASS : The bass is pretty good even at half the volume. The sound doesn't crack even at high volumes. Well this also depends on the audio codec used by your phone. The earbud supports both aptX & LDAC.NOISE CANCELLATION : This is the most surprising aspect of this phone. The noise cancellation is just superb. At 40-50% volume and above, you just don't hear anything but the sound in your earphones. I wouldn't recommend it while driving ;)BLUETOOTH : The Bluetooth 5.0 has a very good range when used with Bluetooth 5.0 capable phones. I use it with One Plus 5 and it's awesome.

body: Let me tell you in the beginning that I rarely give any product five star as I think no product can be perfect and there is always a room for improvement. Please read patiently to the end behind this exception.Let me first review the product. I am using it for about 10 days continuously.Build Quality:- Earphone build quality is good. However the casing(battery charger) requires major improvement. The cap of the charger is flimsy and is prone to be broken easily if not handled properly. The earphone sits in the casing and is magnetic which will not allow the earphone to get dropped. The build quality of the part is good and will charge your earphone about 30-35 times in the real world scenario.Rating(4/5)Audio quality:- If anybody is looking to buy this product solely for music, then I will suggest go blindly for it., especially for the BASS lovers. You will not have much complaint in that regard, when you are getting the product in such price bracket. Sadly, I cannot say the same thing about the MIDS and trebles which are OK and can be considered as good in comparison to price in which it is being offered. However, if you are looking to use this for calling and receiving the calls, then this is far from expectation. Donâ€™t get me wrong, it will serve your purpose, however occasionally people from the other end has complaint about the muffle voice coming. Seller, definitely needs to improve its product in this regard. I wanted to use it for the music solely, hence no issue for me.For Music:- (4/5)For Call:- (3.5/5)Connectivity:- This is one of the area where it has truly surprised me. I have a 2000 sq feet house and  the earphone remains connected even to the far corner of my house, while my mobile is lying in another corner. But, you need to understand, connectivity will definitely hampers, if the no. of walls increases between the devices. Moreover, it seamlessly gets connected to phone, tablet, laptop and smart tvâ€™s. I have checked on all of them and face no problems whatsoever.  Rating(5/5)Comfortability, Duration and noise cancellation:- One full battery charge of the earphone will easily last you for about 3 hours. You will not face any kind of inconvenience while wearing them for long hours, but please make sure to use the correct size of earbuds(Total 4 sizes have been provided in the box). Please do not use while swimming and bathing(sweats are OK). The earphone will not fallout  while doing casual workout like running, heavy weight lifting, cardioâ€™s etc. Noise cancellation is excellent. Rating(4.5/5)After Sale Support:- Absolutely Fabulous !!. and this the reason behind giving 5 star to this product. The first product which I had received was faulty and I have returned the product on the same day. After giving the feedback, the seller has gone out of its way and contacted me again to give another chance and review the product with free shipping. This shows the confidence of the seller over his product and I gladly accepted it as we all know that one or two pieces can have manufacturing defect which can be true even for branded product. The next piece which was sent worked flawlessly, but I was more happy with the attitude of the seller who were always eager to hear our complaints and feedback in a positive manner and trying to rectify the issues as much as possible. Rating(5/5)As a customer we always wanted bang for our bucks and a peace of mind about the quality which has been promptly provided by the seller. What more you can ask now !!If this review has helped you in any way, please upvote  and if you have any questions related to this product or anything which has not been covered here, please feel free to comment.
title: Fantastic Seller: Go for it!!
